<li>1888/89, "<a href="https://en.wikisource.org/wiki/Electromagnetic_effects_of_a_moving_charge" class="extiw" title="s:Electromagnetic effects of a moving charge">Electromagnetic waves, the propagation of potential, and the electromagnetic effects of a moving charge</a>", <i>The Electrician</i>.</li>
<li>1889, "<a href="https://en.wikisource.org/wiki/Motion_of_Electrification_through_a_Dielectric" class="extiw" title="s:Motion of Electrification through a Dielectric">On the Electromagnetic Effects due to the Motion of Electrification through a Dielectric</a>", <i>Phil.Mag.S.5</i> 27: 324.</li>
